main event: A reported UFO sighting occurred in Crossett, Arkansas on June 23, 1960, involving a brilliant object traveling at high speed.
interesting points: The object was observed for about 5 seconds before it disappeared., The sighting may be related to an Air Force plane making low passes in the area., The witness described the object as brilliant and reflective against the dark sky., Similar descriptions have been noted in meteor sightings in nearby Louisiana., The report was submitted to the Air Tactical Intelligence Center for further analysis.
witness description: One civilian witness reported the sighting; additional information was provided by a person from the Air Tactical Intelligence Center.
